N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11ยง 23.1 - Applications

State Regulations

The forms of applications for licenses to act as insurance agents pursuant to section
2115
of the Insurance Law are hereby prescribed as follows: individuals; partnerships or associations; corporations; limited liability companies. These forms may be obtained upon request by insurers to the Insurance Department, Albany, NY. Notes
